text: Alfie Buller (born 12 August 1957) is an Irish equestrian. He competed in the team eventing at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Irish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Ireland Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
